-- Popolare Milano May Appoint Piero Montani as CEO, Sole Reports
-- B y   C h i a r a   R e m o n d i n i
-- 2012-01-07T12:05:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-07/popolare-milano-may-appoint-piero-montani-as-ceo-sole-reports.html
Banca Popolare di Milano Scarl (PMI)  may
appoint Piero Montani as chief executive officer,  Il Sole 24 Ore 
reported today, without saying how it got the information.  The supervisory board of the cooperative bank is scheduled
to meet Jan. 10 to discuss the appointment, the daily reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Chiara Remondini in Milan at 
 cremondini@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kenneth Wong at 
 kwong11@bloomberg.net  